<p>However, even if the cache manager has a protected</p>

<p>protected $_caches = array();</p>

<p>it doesn't offer any way to return back all the caches (or caches names).</p>

<p>This could be useful in certain situations, i would only mention the need to cleanup all the caches...</p>

